  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK361">
<l>avāveṉpa vellā vuyirkkumeñ ñāṉṟun</l>
<l>tavāap piṟappīṉum vittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The wise) say that the seed, which produces unceasing births, at all times, to all creatures, is desire.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
